175
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:31,350
Thank you, Mister.

176
00:12:45,910 --> 00:12:47,240
Liuying.

177
00:12:47,590 --> 00:12:49,240
Don’t you remember Dragon King

178
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:51,030
