267
00:20:00,910 --> 00:20:05,230
♪There’s regret when we part♪

268
00:20:06,390 --> 00:20:11,390
♪Feelings get me stuck in loneliness♪

269
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:17,320
♪I’m waiting to meet you again♪

270
00:20:17,630 --> 00:20:23,440
